   version stable 1.0.2 1.0.1 1.0.0
   require gcc-g++
      opts --enable-static=no
  category graphic
 attribute library makej multilib-concurrent
    source http://savannah.nongnu.org/download/openexr/ilmbase-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info home  http://www.openexr.com/
      info docs  http://www.openexr.com/documentation.html
      info mail  http://www.openexr.com/mailinglist.html
  estimate 900
      desc 'libraries that openexr uses

IlmThread is a thread abstraction library for
use with OpenEXR and other software packages.
It currently supports pthreads and Windows threads.

Imath implements 2D and 3D vectors, 3x3 and 4x4 matrices,
quaternions and other useful 2D and 3D math functions.

Iex is an exception-handling library.'

build(){
case $VERSION in
 1.0.2) sed -i '1i#include <cstring>' Imath/ImathMatrix.h ;;
esac
default_build
}
